rdfs:label: SlamHeader
omn:EquivalentTo: HedHeader and (inHedSchema some SlamSchema) and (version value "1.0.0") and (library value "slam") and (withStandard value "8.3.0") and (unmerged value "True")

rdfs:label: SlamPrologue
dc:description: The HED SLAM(Sensor Location and Motion) HED library schema is designed to standardize the annotation of sensor locations and human motion across recording modalities and diverse fields.
